	<div class="ideas">
		<div class="container">
   			<h4>Date 1: The Classic</h4>
    			<p>You eat for sixteen hours a day, so a classic date for you and your new panda friend to enjoy is a special meal! Dine on the finest leaves, stems and shoots and show your date you're a true bamboo connoisseur. The Classic date is great for Bamboo Buddies looking to meet someone special. </p>
    		<div class="classic">
