    	</div>
		<div class="container">
    		<h4>Date 2: The Active</h4>
    			<p>You've both been sitting around all day, so how about some time 	to stretch your legs? Visit a new patch of forest and go climbing for a more active date. Race to the top and show your competitive streak! The Active date is great for Bamboo Buddies looking to get active this mating season. </p>
    		<div class="active">
    		<img src ="http://media.npr.org/programs/atc/features/2008/may/chengdu_panda/climbing540-85d1d63bb9224f3c926e188fbc19a4a09e4947ec.jpg" class="center"/>
    	</div>
		<div class="container">
    		<h4>Date 3: The Romantic</h4>
    			<p>If you're a quiet kind of panda, maybe you want to keep things low-key while you get to know each other. How about taking your new panda friend on a walk through your favourite spots in the forest? Show them your thinking spot, where you like to eat, or just somewhere scenic! The Romantic date is great for Bamboo Buddies looking for something meaningful. </p>
